      </para>
      <para id="id14032364">The learner will be able to make informed decisions about further study and career choices.</para>
      <para id="id14521206">
        <emphasis effect="italics">We know this when the learner:</emphasis>
      </para>
      <para id="id4253991">5.1 identifies and discusses career and study choices and their corresponding requirements;</para>
      <para id="id14617133">5.2 investigates career and study opportunities related to own interests and abilities.</para>
